name: Nanakusa Nazuna | Yofukashi no Uta
description:
LoRA is generated entirely from anime images.
Should work well with any model. NSFW works nicely too.

To recreate her hair with tags 'hair rings' (default hair) and 'long hair' (unbraided hair).
Maid, Swimsuit, Nurse outfits are also more easily recreatable with correct tags.

I recommend latest version (v3) :)

Check samples for prompts :)

Leave a like, comment, review but first of all, ENJOY ;)
